      "id": "1482545927704150149",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-15T01:08:13.536+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "If you guys are still having trouble with openocd running on RPI we got it working to our jtag taps (which are standard) as well as to ibex and I can share the instructions for our pi zero wireless ones.",
      "author": {
        "id": "1034663307598123049",
        "name": "wspitts2",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "beardothaweirdo",
